data.title: Samantha Stosur
data.text:
Nicknames: Sammy, Queenslander, Brisbane Native

Sam was born in Brisbane, is now calling Sydney as her homebase in Australia. She has a United States home in Tampa.

Click here for Sam's website

Current Ranking: 73 - (Highest ranking of 4 in 2011 in singles)

WTA player of the month July 2015

US Open Sportsmanship Award 2012
